# Attendees

- Belio C. Sinangote
- Project Team

---

# Agenda

- Review project progress
- Demonstrate AI Knowledge Base Sync workflow
- Discuss AI document analysis
- Review Notion integration
- Identify current issues and blockers
- Define action items

---

# Discussion Notes

The team reviewed the AI Knowledge Base Sync workflow developed using n8n.

A demonstration showed how the workflow automatically detects newly uploaded PDF documents from Google Drive, extracts their contents, and uses AI to analyze the text.

The AI successfully generated a document title, concise summary, category, tags, and keywords before synchronizing the information into a structured Notion Knowledge Base.

The workflow also sent Telegram notifications after each successful document synchronization.

Testing confirmed that the workflow can automate document organization and significantly reduce manual documentation efforts.

