# AI Integration Updates

- Successfully connected OpenRouter AI.
- Structured JSON output is generated for every processed document.
- AI extracts:
  - Title
  - Summary
  - Category
  - Tags
  - Keywords

---

# Issues & Blockers

- Initial Structured Output Parser configuration required adjustments.
- Notion database permissions had to be updated before synchronization.
- Duplicate detection is planned for a future version.

---

# Decisions Made

- Continue using Notion as the centralized knowledge base.
- Store AI-generated metadata for every uploaded document.
- Expand the workflow with semantic search capabilities in future releases.

